                            </author>
                            <title xml:lang="ota-Latn-x" key="">Tarjuma-i Pand-náma-i 'Attár</title>
                            <title key="tr">Tercüme-i Pend-i Attâr</title>
                            <title xml:lang="fa">ترجمه پندنامه عطار</title>
                            <note>A metrical Turkish translation, in the original's metre, of the
                                <title key="work_20152">Pand-náma</title> of <persName role="ant" key="person_120724759">Farídu'd-Dín
                                    'Attár</persName>, dedicated to Prince Báyazíd, son of Sultán
